@startuml Sequence_Admin_AccountVerification
title Quản Trị - Xác Thực Tài Khoản

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant AuthService as "Auth\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Xác Thực Ứng Viên ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Xác thực tài khoản"
FrontEnd -> AuthService: GET /api/admin/candidates/pending
AuthService -> Database: Query tai_khoan (status=PENDING)
Database --> AuthService: List pending candidates
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Candidates list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách

Admin -> FrontEnd: Chọn ứng viên
FrontEnd -> AuthService: GET /api/admin/candidates/{id}
AuthService -> Database: Get candidate info
Database --> AuthService: Candidate details
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Details
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem chi tiết

Admin -> FrontEnd: Xác thực
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/admin/candidates/{id}/verify
AuthService -> Database: Update status = ACTIVE
Database --> AuthService: OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Verified
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Xác thực thành công

== Xác Thực Nhà Tuyển Dụng ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Chọn tab "Nhà tuyển dụng"
FrontEnd -> AuthService: GET /api/admin/recruiters/pending
AuthService -> Database: Query pending recruiters
Database --> AuthService: List
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Recruiters list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách

Admin -> FrontEnd: Chọn nhà tuyển dụng
FrontEnd -> AuthService: GET /api/admin/recruiters/{id}
AuthService -> Database: Get recruiter info
Database --> AuthService: Details
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Info
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem chi tiết

Admin -> FrontEnd: Xác thực
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/admin/recruiters/{id}/verify
AuthService -> Database: Update status = ACTIVE
Database --> AuthService: OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Verified
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Xác thực thành công

== Từ Chối Xác Thực ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Từ chối"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show reason form
Admin -> FrontEnd: Nhập lý do từ chối
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/admin/accounts/{id}/reject\n(reason)
AuthService -> Database: Update status = REJECTED
Database --> AuthService: OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Rejected
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Từ chối thành công

@enduml
